{"tid":157554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"各位絲打著裙個時會唔會掃裙?","createTime":"2017-03-15T14:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T07:59:26.000Z","uid":28905,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd1183789da3917327fbf39c10fd54dba90576e","tid":157554,"uid":28905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"[其實之前開過架啦]<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁問? 以前阿媽教落著裙要掃平左先好坐, 係佢地面前我一定斯斯文文啦, 但平時我係鐘意咁樣嘅 (偷人地張圖用用先)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/759795v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F759795v.jpg&h=935de2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係坐圓凳個D, 直情會將個裙擺圍住張凳咁坐添。<br />\n<br />\n自從多左人著legging之後, 可能因為有legging或者絲襪隔一隔, 都會就咁坐而唔會掃。<br />\n<br />\n你地著裙坐個時會係雙手掃到條裙平晒先? 定係唔多理坐左先算呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2f6c7308feed771fb50eda549d44bba2689e66","tid":157554,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"細菌入西"},{"pid":"c7a1e8dcd5b9bc4e05a06b2bc7709d5b87caba1f","tid":157554,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔係絲打 但我都會掃左先坐"},{"pid":"4446be026ad205c5a586e725aaab49b8f2096e7b","tid":157554,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"咁醜怪㗎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e0ef252b5da37125024eef98ca4c1a7b0ef1c1","tid":157554,"uid":82425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"會 無條裙墊一墊個pat pat好凍/好吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3862b6578253dfee4b065d72c951b35cf288e8","tid":157554,"uid":30563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"睇咩場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19ca02ceab36cb9c625169ffe2aa8d215384a91","tid":157554,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,